text: Bagmati is a river in Nepal. Bagmati may also refer to: * Bagmati Pradesh, one of 7 provinces of Nepal * Bagmati, Lalitpur, rural municipality in Lalitpur District in Province No. 3 of Nepal * Bagmati, Sarlahi, a municipality in Sarlahi District in Province No. 2 of Nepal * Bagmati Zone, a former zone in Nepal == See also == * Bhagmati Express
title: Bagmati (disambiguation)
